$interpreted: Ralph: Princess, surrender now or I'll have no choice but to kill the boy!
Ralph: You're the girl from the Feather Clan...
Angelia: I remember you. You're Nigel's friend... the wings on your back...
Yamitsuki: Not out of danger yet, stay focused!
Yamitsuki: ...Nigel's debts are paid. You two are even from now on.
Angelia: Nigel? He's still alive? Is he alright?
Angelia: Did Nigel ask you to do this? Or was this your own decision...
Angelia: ...Nigel, what are you? Friend or foe...
Royal Infantry Captain: There they are, get 'em!
